+1 [ICON_Food] Food, +1 [ICON_Production] Production for the city center tile and the mountain tiles in the adjacent area. Citizens [ICON_Citizen] can work in mountains with output. [NEWLINE]+1% all-type output for each [ICON_Citizen] in the city. In cities of [ICON_Religion] religion, [ICON_Citizen] of the same religion provide it instead; if [ICON_Religion] is the dominant religion, [ICON_Citizen] of the same religion provide an additional +2% all-type output. (Excluding [ICON_Food] food)
Unconditionally goodwilled to all civilizations, but extremely disgusted with civilizations that value space race and global travel.

The Circle Gods are calling! Kaia Kalons, ever since the Circle Gods from the celestial bodies came and performed miracles one after another, Esanaqin has been a loyal servant of the Circle Gods. In order to lead the people of this world to the Principle of the Circle, you have been chosen to be the driver of the Circle Gods and pass on the methods of the Circle Gods to perform miracles... Of course, the most important thing is to keep this world well for the Circle Gods.

The city receives bonuses from all nearby regional buildings. In areas adjacent to mountains, the range of its regional buildings extends by 3 tiles. [NEWLINE]Has the unique Holy Land project "Circle God Drive". Has the unique Holy Land wonder "Area 1551". [NEWLINE]Each turn, each city can sacrifice a unit with [ICON_Charges] labor times to advance the progress of a regional project. Once the project is completed, it provides a builder for your [ICON_Capital] capital.

Kaia Kalons's Special Wonder: An Industrial Age wonder unlocked by "Flight". It requires a Holy Land and can be built without being placed in a cell. It can be purchased with [ICON_Faith] Faith as a Holy Land building. [NEWLINE] Unlock the Space Center in advance after studying Astrology. Build Space Centers 10 times faster when there are no Space Centers in the country. Cities with Space Centers gain +7 [ICON_Power] Clean Energy Power, and each population in them provides +1.5 [ICON_Science] Science. The time required to run Space Race projects is halved.

There are only three things you should pay attention to here: [NEWLINE] Don't look at what you shouldn't look at; [NEWLINE] Don't listen to what you shouldn't listen to; [NEWLINE] Don't say what you shouldn't say. [NEWLINE]——《Guidelines for Visitors in Area 1551》

Kaia Kalons's special sanctuary project. [NEWLINE]Gain a large amount of [ICON_Gold] and [ICON_Faith] during operation. Upon completion, gain [ICON_Science] equal to 150% of the current [ICON_Faith] and [ICON_Gold] output respectively. [NEWLINE]Can only be run in one city at a time.

Replaces "Apostle". Immune to [ICON_Religion] combat power loss caused by injury. Can completely eliminate other religious forces. [NEWLINE] Adjacent hostile units will have -5 [ICON_Damaged] health points per turn when they are close to your border.

Unlocks "Mining", must be built in a mountain tile, immune to disasters and pillage. Allows units to travel through mountains, allowing the [ICON_TradeRoute] trade route to gain multiple [ICON_Gold] gold from the target city's area. [NEWLINE]+0.5 [ICON_Housing] Housing, +1 [ICON_Housing] Housing after unlocking "Engineering". [NEWLINE]+1 [ICON_Production] Production. Gain +1 [ICON_Food] Food from adjacent areas. Gain +1 [ICON_Science] Science from adjacent Conclaves after unlocking "Education".

You are right, but the Circle Gods are a group of flying disc-shaped angels descended from the Circle Principle. The story begins after Theia rammed Gaia. Long ago, the civilizations chosen by the Circle Gods were granted the "Super Model Power" and ascended to a new level of strength. You will become a leader, starting from the first bud of life underwater, encountering various barbarians, and engaging in hearty battles with them to defend your ascended assets - at the same time, gain the favor of the Circle Gods.

Essanathin places great emphasis on population, and building areas, including the city center, next to mountains helps to obtain food. Under the leadership of Kaia Kallons, new projects can also bring considerable benefits. Both scientific and religious victories are their strengths.

Esanaqin values ​​population and religion, and disrupting their religious beliefs can slightly curb their gains. But obviously the best solution is to just crush them, as they have no advantage in combat. Just be careful to avoid being adjacent to Celestial Apostles at the end of the turn.
Nice to meet you, stranger, I am the chieftain of the blessed Esanaqin, you can call me Kaia Kallons.
If you would like to visit our city, there is indeed an area that is temporarily open for you.
There is some distance between our cities, could you please share with us the location of the capital?
I will bring them to see Yuan Shen.
Today is a more important day for Esanaqin than the day when we receive you.
In order to spread the gospel of Yuan Shen, I have arranged some delegations to perform live performances for you, all of which are miracles that can turn stone into gold...
That fool's gold can still earn you some money...
Please allow us to establish a permanent embassy.
Yuan Shen will be very happy.
As long as you don't run around randomly, we can still live in peace...
In compliance with the will of the God Yuan, I ask you to temporarily open the border to Esanqin.
The round god is pleased to see us value harmony.
At this moment? You are not kidding.
There is no need for us to be hostile, so why don't we declare friendship?
The round god is pleased to see us value harmony.
At this moment? You are not kidding.
We can definitely further our mutual benefit, so come and establish an alliance with us.
As a human being, harmony is the most important thing.
He wanted to make a fortune quietly.
Do you want to steal my Yuanshen? ! ! ! !
Your military forces near Essanqin are increasing in number, and some of us are worried about it... Please transfer your troops.
You can say whatever you want as long as it doesn't affect the peace between us.
You little bastard, you have no manners. Be careful or I will do something bad to you! [NEWLINE](Condemn you)
Our warriors can truly ascend to the Circle of Truth after death, but your warriors can only rot miserably in fantasy.
If you disrespect Yuan Shen, you will be killed!
The round god is pleased to see us value harmony.
It seems that you haven't realized where you are wrong.
Stop, stop, stop! I've lost this war! Stop it!

The most severe Yuanshen addiction attack, I lay in bed, desperately chanting Yuanshen, grabbing my chest in pain, thinking that fighting a battle would be fine, but in the end I could no longer serve Yuanshen, my heart hurt more and more as if it was about to explode, I desperately slapped myself in the face and hated my own incompetence, the harder I slapped, the more I slapped, the more tears came out of my eyes, I really didn't know what to do, I really missed Yuanshen so much that I was going crazy. [NEWLINE]I would think of Yuanshen when I lay in bed, I would think of Yuanshen when I took a shower, I would think of Yuanshen when I went out, I would think of Yuanshen when I walked, I would think of Yuanshen when I rode in a carriage, I would think of Yuanshen when I worked, I would think of Yuanshen when I fought, I would stare at the word Yuanshen, I stared at the word Yuanshen every moment, I really felt like I was possessed, my thoughts about Yuanshen seemed to be pathological, I was so lonely! Really so lonely! Why is there not one life in this universe that belongs to me? Do you know? Every night, my eyes are burning, I am sick and I want to look at Yuan Shen like crazy, I want to look at Yuan Shen fiercely, my eyes can't bear it, Yuan Shen, my Yuan Shen, take me away, Yuan Shen, I can't stay in this world without Yuan Shen for even a second! [NEWLINE]Please take me to the Circle of Truth!
